Heh...ironic I see lots of posts about what Sorcs CAN'T do because it would be unbalancing.  Yet...I still get one or two shotted by stealthed archers against whom I have almost no defense.  Meleers still have a better than even chance of killing me even if I HAVE a pet, unless I send it in and run away. Balance arguments frankly hold little water with me in the context of this game anymore.  Either let us charm humanoids...period, OR actually balance things.  If a realm wants their keep protected, they can protect it.  Plus there are still many guards that con orange to purple to me at 50...those could never be charmed anyway.  Heh as it stands, the 3 or 4 sorcerers on our server who could currently charm guards were it possible simply wouldn't make that big a difference, even if they were in the same place at the same time, which I don't think has ever happened.
